Ocean Remote Sensing Division

   [fuji3.jpg] Dr. James H. Churnside, Chief
   MISSION:
   Our division conceives and develops new acoustic and electromagnetic
   remote sensing technologies to support NOAA's ocean monitoring charter.
   "In the Hollow of a Wave off the Coast at Kanagawa,"
   a woodblock print by Katsushika Hokusai, 1827
   [noaabullet.gif]

  Research Areas:

